{"tid":1718740,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"灣仔被藍絲啊叔推嘅女手足入一入黎","createTime":"2019-11-14T02:17:41.000Z","updateTime":"2020-04-05T18:19:02.000Z","uid":251192,"like":11,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":21,"replies":[{"pid":"f0feb1879843cb83351fa9de76896818f4c1c4e1","tid":1718740,"uid":251192,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-14T02:17:41.000Z","msg":"頭先係灣仔好似有個阿叔捉你跳閘，之後推左你落樓梯，見到你好似抽搐咁跌落去<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />，之後你就失蹤左，希望你冇事喇<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n其他人已經第一時間衝落去截住嗰推人阿叔，但有第二個阿叔不停保佢，手度仲有個背囊，唔知係咪你嘅<br />\n<br />\n原本有個記者報左警，想用正當途徑去處理<br />\n<br />\n但原來有<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">個保人嗰個阿叔係休班狗</span><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />，call左一隊防暴黎護送佢地走，仲好似會告返你襲擊警務人員<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n阿叔之後蒙住面咁俾隊防暴保護走。<br />\n<br />\n所以當冇左個背囊喇，小心啲，之後唔知會發生咩事，我怕個背囊入面有嘢會揾到你，或者揾定律師<br />\n<br />\n推人啊叔<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/4niPGet.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F4niPGet.png&h=e1816d62&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/ZL4LezC.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FZL4LezC.png&h=c40440b2&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2019/11/14/101518_a7cfbbf1aa5c4812ad2359ef93da5747.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2019%2F11%2F14%2F101518_a7cfbbf1aa5c4812ad2359ef93da5747.png&h=f4a87759&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"d56842c375b00759